{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 ARKITEKT\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b A REAPER toolkit for general use with emphasis on music design, scoring and game audio.}\line Specialized workflow scripts (e.g., Region Playlist, Theme Adjuster) + a reusable {\b ReaImGui} components library with a flexible {\b theme system}.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Developed by {\b ARKADATA}.\par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Install (via ReaPack)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab Install {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://reapack.com/"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
ReaPack
}}}
.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 2.\tx360\tab In REAPER: {\b Extensions \u8594 ? ReaPack \u8594 ? Import repositories\u8230 ?}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 3.\tx360\tab Paste this URL and confirm:\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \f1 https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ARKADATAazk/ARKITEKT/main/index.xml\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 4.\tx360\tab {\b Browse packages} \u8594 ? install what you need \u8594 ? {\b Sync packages} to update.\sa180\par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 What\u8217's inside\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Apps}\line Scripts focused on real workflows (e.g., {\i Region Playlist}, {\i Color Palette}, theme utilities).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b ReaImGui Widgets (Library)}\line A modular UI kit (chips, pads, grids, tiles, status bars, etc.) used across apps.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Theme System}\line Centralized colors/skins with presets and per-app overrides for consistent styling.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li720 \fi0 Action names appear as {\b \u8220"ARK: \u8230 ?\u8221"} in REAPER. Filenames follow {\f1 ARK_<Feature>.lua}.\par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
